          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Maison Brondeau different from other wine stores?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Maison Brondeau is an independent wine and spirits shop in White Plains, NY focused on hospitality, education, and discovery. Our team carefully curates wines and spirits from around the world, ranging from everyday favorites to rare and collectible bottles. We believe wine should be approachable, and we help customers find the perfect bottle for any occasion, budget, or level of wine knowledge.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_PmLcKD": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where is Maison Brondeau located?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Maison Brondeau is located right in the heart of Westchester, in White Plains, New York. Just steps from the Metro North train station on Main Street, our shop offers a carefully selected collection of red, white, rose and sparkling wines, as well as whiskey, vodka, tequila, gin, rum and other premium spirits and canned cocktails.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
